trans-unit.source: Defines a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement"></xref> objects.
Gets the number of elements in the collection.
An <xref:System.Int32> representing the number of elements in the collection.
Gets a collection of elements by their name.

While the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Id%2A> property of an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement> must be unique, multiple elements can use the same <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Name%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 동안는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Id%2A>속성의는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement>해야 고유 하므로 여러 요소 צ ְ ײ 동일한 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Name%2A>속성.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Name%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Id%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name or ID of the element.
An containing the elements whose property match name.
trans-unit.target: 요소가 포함 된 해당 속성 일치 name .

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through a collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션을 반복 하는 열거자를 반환 합니다.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> that can be used to iterate through the collection.
Gets an item from the collection by specifying its numerical index.
trans-unit.target: 숫자 인덱스를 지정 하 여 컬렉션에서 항목을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: Elements in an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElementCollection> are not guaranteed to be in source code order.
In other words, just because a `DIV` element is the first element inside of a `BODY` tag does not mean that the first element of the collection will be the `DIV` element.
trans-unit.target: 즉, 때문에 `DIV` 요소는 내부에 첫 번째 요소는 `BODY` 태그 의미가 컬렉션의 첫 번째 요소 됩니다는 `DIV` 요소입니다.

trans-unit.source: The position from which to retrieve an item from the collection.
An item from the collection by specifying its numerical index.
trans-unit.target: 숫자 인덱스를 지정 하 여 컬렉션의 항목입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets an item from the collection by specifying its name.
trans-unit.target: 해당 이름을 지정 하 여 컬렉션에서 항목을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Name*> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement.Id*> attribute of the element.
An <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElement"></xref>, if the named element is found.
Otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
Copies the elements of the collection to an <xref:System.Array>, starting at a particular <xref:System.Array> index.
The one-dimensional <xref:System.Array> that is the destination of the elements copied from collection.
The <xref:System.Array> must have zero-based indexing.
The zero-based index in `array` at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: 인덱스는&0;부터 시작 `array` 복사가 시작 되는 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether access to the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElementCollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe).
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 액세스 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.HtmlElementCollection"> </xref> 이 동기화 되었으면 (스레드로부터 안전 하 게 보호).

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> in all cases.
Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 대 한 액세스를 동기화 하는 데 사용할 수 있는 개체를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: An object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection> 에 대 한 액세스를 동기화 하는 데 사용할 수 있는 개체
